{"tid":2501632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局：考生遇封區應優先檢測 未獲結果下可離開封區前往考場 到步有陰性報告即可應考","createTime":"2021-04-23T13:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T13:46:58.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"97eb9f9e9be9de84a3ab569d808b74ad227dc9fe","tid":2501632,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:39:32.000Z","msg":"教育局：考生若受封區強檢影響 應出示准考證要求優先檢測<br />\n<br />\n教育局指，如果政府封區強檢時，受限區域內有應屆文憑試考生須於翌日參加文憑試，建議考生盡早前往臨時採樣站表明考生身分及提供准考證等，要求優先檢測。如果考生要在解封之前前往試場，無論是否已取得檢測結果，都可向工作人員提出，在核實考生已接受檢測及記錄資料後，將容許考生離開受限區域。只要考生在前往試場期間收到陰性檢測結果，就可以如期應考。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2388668\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2388668&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=2e491ecf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2388668</a>"},{"pid":"b602d95814c699737b3cfe2fded43fecd7e60322","tid":2501632,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 考之前一粒鐘封區，等你趕唔切考試明年請早"},{"pid":"9591a06a7a02eec4fbcedfdb8aa222ef607f49c7","tid":2501632,"uid":54876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"教育局大定popo大？夠膽叫學生離開封區咁大膽？"},{"pid":"6128b784f05dbea35990e1b804da89fe4268339a","tid":2501632,"uid":249979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9591a06a7a02eec4fbcedfdb8aa222ef607f49c7","tid":2501632,"uid":54876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"教育局大定popo大？夠膽叫學生離開封區咁大膽？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:45:06.000Z","msg":"班popo肯定會左拖右拖<br />\n開考咗你都未走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4ca5221b4d8c7f59cc9198559e1692f16b78a3","tid":2501632,"uid":155682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:45:16.000Z","msg":"咁陽性係咪成個場學生去隔離14日，下年再考？"},{"pid":"8add44c896e07283f293044ef75cdb878a60c6b2","tid":2501632,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"未獲結果下可離開 .....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0486c78cce057f928e54a0868c2bb456ac1fca21","tid":2501632,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:46:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">popo: 牙sir做野唔使你教</span>"},{"pid":"3c272b79db1834c4f14047d244d02c843a3a48b0","tid":2501632,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"傾好左唔感染學生"},{"pid":"1ca1cb81b9c2871fa20ddbaa471fc57f49b0399c","tid":2501632,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8add44c896e07283f293044ef75cdb878a60c6b2","tid":2501632,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"未獲結果下可離開 .....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"同人逼巴士逼地鐵冇風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bus_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}